releaseNotes:
New Providers & Health Checks
• Added 8 new providers: Together AI, Venice AI, Qwen (Alibaba), Volcengine (Doubao), BytePlus, Qianfan (Baidu), Xiaomi (MiMo), LiteLLM
• Provider health status dots: green (working), yellow (unreachable), red (dead key/quota), gray (not yet verified)
• "Check All" button verifies all API keys using free endpoints (zero token cost)
• Health tracked passively from real proxy traffic — no extra API calls
• Updated FAQ with health dot explanation
